
Steps to compile and run this application: 

1- Download and install the latest versions of NTL and GMP libraries.

2- Read and follow instructions in INSTALL.txt to download the HElib library and compile it using its Makefile 
(found in HElib/src). Make sure that the "fhe.a" file is created.

3- cd to HElib/src/decision_tree and open the Makefile:

  - change the path to the HElib path on your local machine

  HEdir = /Users/PATH/TO/HElib/src
  
  
4- On the command line:

    cd HElib/src/decision_tree

    make
   
    
 5- To run the code, simply run
 
    ./secComp
    
    




